---
title: Sugar Shack Bison Meatball Poutine with Maple Gravy and Side Salad
description: What's better than poutine? A bison meatball poutine with maple-spiked gravy, of course! Roasted potato wedges are doused in this savoury-sweet gravy and topped with squeaky cheese curds. Garnishes of chives and crispy shallots add brightness and satisfying crunch. A fresh side salad of arugula-spinach mix, tomatoes and maple bacon adds balance to this decadent meal!
